{"tid":1841874,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢各醫院幾近崩潰 醫療物資斷絕","createTime":"2020-01-25T12:10:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T12:26:11.000Z","uid":115538,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c811297fc8f8603e9be896628aed34a76e834c29","tid":1841874,"uid":115538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:10:25.000Z","msg":"仍留守當地的醫護人員在微博、網路上求援，表示因武漢封城，大量物資無法順利進到城內，各醫院醫療用品幾乎用罄，但病人仍不斷湧入，甚至醫護人員在網上崩潰表示，病人都跪著求他們救了，但現在連醫護人員最基本的防護服、面罩都沒了，醫院瀕臨崩潰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/iFNq3kw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FiFNq3kw.jpg&h=b87d8681&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/YSktRgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FYSktRgg.jpg&h=efec7a27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/c4N1fdz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fc4N1fdz.jpg&h=7d2b1b36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上頭高官都跑光了，只剩基層醫護人員硬撐，醫療體系沒有領導。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jJPOLSM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FjJPOLSM.jpg&h=4735b733&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/68dsmzK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F68dsmzK.jpg&h=ed9ea57d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wFU4EuF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FwFU4EuF.jpg&h=19f32ced&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經有醫生精神崩潰了<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dSqYneK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FdSqYneK.jpg&h=aa07b4ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/YBBWjBb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FYBBWjBb.jpg&h=e7390683&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qGyYRTS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqGyYRTS.jpg&h=de7fc0a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://reurl.cc/gvdkLp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2FgvdkLp&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2FTDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=1b060913\" target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/gvdkLp</a><br />\n（網上備份影片來源自Twitter）"},{"pid":"36fd23b039134da9077c0c6a07e92e8a46745996","tid":1841874,"uid":6845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:11:39.000Z","msg":"俾佢班同胞封曬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9761a930af0a0e7fb3e8e070a1338fe17c3b73aa","tid":1841874,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:13:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rvzYA7x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrvzYA7x.jpg&h=cdbda1fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YNPxFzd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYNPxFzd.jpg&h=419a6449&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8bae083fd1d977c75aef0d9055e0c3cfaf0c032","tid":1841874,"uid":127735,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:14:17.000Z","msg":"感性上同情<br />\n理性上無視"},{"pid":"3110c3d9e48e1f8416cda29c6bfed780197eedbd","tid":1841874,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:14:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc53f41fcf2e6e5fe30880a6abe1a5c91bf6d71d","tid":1841874,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:18:17.000Z","msg":"解放軍十幾年前地震表演過空投能力,<br />\n<br />\n而家空投口罩做下樣都唔識"},{"pid":"1a0494ef691637e65c2c57bc5b678ea6b4e28ddd","tid":1841874,"uid":197069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:22:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dff4fad2295edeb819bcd2341905dd8526ea56b7","tid":1841874,"uid":197069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:22:05.00